      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Bertrand Russell Quote&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;https://www.brainyquote.com/photos_tr/en/b/bertrandrussell/383143/bertrandrussell1-2x.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
