&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;A rose by any other name would smell as sweet&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/images/a-rose-by-any-other-name-would-smell-as-sweet.webp&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
